<h3>Pingry COVID-19 Update</h3>
<h5>A change has been noted on your quarantine status</h5>
<hr/>

<p>Dear <%= "#{@student.first_name} #{@student.last_name}"%>,</p>

<p>According to Pingry's records, you are currently in a 14 day quarantine. The updated status of your quarantine is listed below:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Date of Exposure: <%= @quarantine.exposure %></li>
    <li>Date of Completion: <%= @quarantine.exposure + 14 %></li>
    <li>Status: <%= if @quarantine.completed
            "Complete"    
        else 
            "Incomplete"
        end %></li>
</ul>

<p>If you begin developing symptoms or have any other changes in quarantine status, please contact <a href="mailto:ecarannante@pingry.org">contacttracing@pingry.org</a>. Please note that you will only be permitted to return to campus once the "Status" field reads <strong>"Complete."</strong></p>

<p>Thank you for your help in keeping Pingry safe!</p>
<p>The Pingry School</p>
